OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A sample of hair belonging to the      
OL,6, legendary 19th century Native American 
OL,7, leader Sitting Bull has allowed        
OL,8, scientists to confirm that a South     
OL,9, Dakota man is his great-grandson.      
OL,11,FScientists took DNA from a tiny sample 
OL,12,Fof Sitting Bull's hair that had been   
OL,13,Fstored in Washington DC.               
OL,15,FIt showed that Ernie LaPointe, 73, is  
OL,16,Fhis great-grandson.                    
OL,18,FThe new method allows analysis of      
OL,19,Ffamily lineages with DNA fragments from
OL,20,Flong-dead people.                      
